<div><head>王韶之孝子傳</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.2">王韶之孝子傳<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.3">周青，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.4">東郡人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.5">母患積年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.6">青扶持左右，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.7">身體羸瘦，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.8">村里乃歛錢營助湯藥。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.9">母痊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.10">許嫁同郡周小君。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.11">疾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.12">未獲成禮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.13">乃求見青，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.14">屬累父母，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.15">青許之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.16">俄而命終。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.17">青供養為務十年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.18">中翁姑感之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.19">勸令更嫁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.20">青誓以匪石，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.21">翁姑並自殺。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.22">女姑告青害殺收考，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.23">遂以誣款，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.24">七月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.25">刑青於市，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.26">青謂監殺者曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.27">「乞樹長竿，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.28">繫白旛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.29">青若殺翁姑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.30">血入泉；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.31">不殺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.32">血上天。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.33">既斬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.34">乃緣竿上天。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-1a.35">《御覽》四百十五、六百五十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.2">李陶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.3">交阯人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.4">母終，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.5">陶居於墓側，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.6">躬自治墓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.7">不受鄰人助。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.8">群鳥銜塊助成墳。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.9">《藝文類聚》九十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.10">竺彌，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.11">字道倫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.12">本外國人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.13">居吳興。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.14">父母亡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.15">哀痛瘠毀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.16">冬不衣襦衿。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1328_CHANT_001-2a.17">《書鈔‧襦》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
